<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.2.5">
<l>vantāy pōlē vantumeṉ maṉattiṉainī</l>
<l>cintāmal ceyyā yituvē yituvākil</l>
<l>kontār kāyāviṉ koḻumalart tiruniṟatta</l>
<l>ventāyyā ṉuṉṉai yeṅkuvan taṇukiṟpaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although coming it is like you don’t come. Act you so that</l>
<l>my mind is not scattered. If this is this only,</l>
<l>o our father with the luminous colour of the rich blosoom of the ironwood tree</l>
<l>full of clusters, when shall I come [and] reach you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
